The '''Tratlin''' were a sentient species. The species' members included [[Rallan]], an elderly operative for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] who served as [[Executive officer/Legends|First Officer]] of [[Sandwind Team (Sriluur)|Sandwind Team]].<ref name="SSR">''[[Secrets of the Sisar Run]]''</ref>

